{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a two-column storytelling section focused on emotional gifting psychology.
    
    Left side: soft lifestyle imagery of the Rose Teddy Bear in a romantic setting (bedroom, candlelight, soft shadows).
    
    Right side: copy-driven emotional persuasion.
    
    Headline: “For The Person Who Means Everything.”
    
    Bullet points framed as emotional outcomes, not features:
    – Makes her feel genuinely chosen
    – Lasts longer than flowers
    – Becomes a keepsake, not clutter
    
    Include subtle animated dividers using thin heart outlines that softly fade in on scroll.
    
    Add a small “Perfect For:” row with icons:
    Valentine’s Day • Anniversary • First ‘I Love You’ • Long-Distance Surprise
    
    Include a soft secondary CTA button: “Make Her Day Unforgettable”
    
    Maintain luxury tone, whitespace, slow reveal animations only., make the background translucent, make the background pale pink like the rest of the website
{% enddoc %}
